          It is the classification of data items in programming.
        >> Variable store the different types of data/value so it is important to known about which data types of value store by variable.

 <::> 𝙅𝙖𝙫𝙖 𝙙𝙖𝙩𝙖 𝙩𝙮𝙥𝙚 -->>  
         :: Java writes a code with data types and value.
         :: Java has different text type(numeric , alpha , character), each text contain different data types.

   <::> 𝐃𝐚𝐭𝐚 𝐭𝐲𝐩𝐞𝐬 𝐭𝐞𝐥𝐥𝐬 𝐈𝐧𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 <|>

        >> The Size of Memory Location.
        >> The maximum & minimun value of range that can store in Memory location.
        >> Different types of operation done on memory location.

