  <.𝟏.> 𝙋𝙧𝙞𝙢𝙞𝙩𝙞𝙫𝙚 𝘿𝙖𝙩𝙖 𝙩𝙮𝙥𝙚𝙨 -->>
             > Primitive data types are predefined by the java language.
             > It provide by the java. Out of the box.
             > It has 8 data types.

